{"tid":1425552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急問】差佬圍住，一個搭你膊頭可以點做？","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:50:54.000Z","uid":285873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30e38d7b2b6df7061cf77e67bfebc85c6a7817a3","tid":1425552,"uid":285873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:41:04.000Z","msg":"我發夢睇浸大學生會會長條片時，片段入面個便衣又搭住佢膊頭，隻左手仲伸晒過去攬頸，如果無街坊手足影住，我諗都唔知俾班便衣質幾多下？<br />\n<br />\n所以大家錄影既證據係好緊要，有人影住，班友驚俾人起底，終有一日輪到自己受番，要係法官面前被清算，先至會稍稍收斂，但各位手足影還影，真係要注意安全，因為會越黎越猖獗。"},{"pid":"0463f6a4707c37225e5480ee842b39d37575c6dc","tid":1425552,"uid":23392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:42:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非禮呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"d693e82e215abc91372a30603697c48b95cea985","tid":1425552,"uid":26013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>幫手入去推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時勢唔好好清理一下思緒一個唔覺意就會走歪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1419472/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1419472/page/1</a></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"41f5003ca905989c5bc463d4b57c3dafd3f3e646","tid":1425552,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:46:31.000Z","msg":"詳細可參考巴塞演藝學員成員既做法"},{"pid":"8556193f5b3a5c5f4cdac7af0cc9b0c7cf831bc7","tid":1425552,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:50:54.000Z","msg":"要盡快做私人檢控"}]}